Package ui.drawing.composition

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OrderedSectionComposer<T extends Section>
    Provides a z index to give certain sections priority over others.
    SectionComposer<T extends Section>
    Represents a collections of sections with positions that can be specified that are drawn together.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicSectionComposer<T extends Section>
    Stores a map of coordinates to sections and assembles each row dynamically using each section's getRow method and a filler character.
    BasicSectionGrid<T extends U,​U extends Section>
    Implementation for a BasicSectionComposer.
    Contains a reference grid of sections in a section composer.
    Represents a section that can be drawn to the terminal window.
    BufferedSectionComposer<T extends BufferedSection>

    Represents a section that can be drawn to the terminal window.
